  <h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Cultural stories</li>
    <li>Adventure highlights</li>
    <li>Personal experiences from contributors</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How Posting Works</h2>
  <p>Anyone can create, edit, and share a post without creating an account. That keeps the experience simple and lets travelers contribute quickly while memories are still fresh.</p>
